{"tid":1051614,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"蕭sir教唱歌","createTime":"2019-03-07T17:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T17:10:52.000Z","uid":114955,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"62af41eacada0851ed1cc2a093ee96a2943c82ff","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:30:58.000Z","msg":"我係蕭sir<br />\n流行曲歌唱老師<br />\n<br />\n本人研習外國新派流行聲樂法<br />\n雖唱歌呢件事博大精深 一生未能精通<br />\n只小有心得<br />\n大家有興趣就問下<br />\n我識就答下<br />\n<br />\n講明係流行曲<br />\n古典派嘅朋友仔就不喜勿進<br />\n我講到嘅嘢可能會同古典聲樂火星撞地球<br />\n<br />\n有性趣請回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2cd053b64c8dc302737d155102bd25d450bf4c","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"用文字嚟做教學基本上係冇咩好大嘅作用<br />\n但盡量解譯概念同釐清謬誤<br />\n亦都可能會推介啲yt片俾大家睇下"},{"pid":"5467c3ba9eed7530e3f81f00920f0c7c2f528330","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:34:37.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月會忙到爆<br />\n啲問題可能要慢慢覆<br />\n請見諒"},{"pid":"29c75d32666273b042061454675237a56bd4ca86","tid":1051614,"uid":110519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"你係混音派 定真 假音斷層派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"d8485f553a7e7bec2e2fc1795655b2c6f492cc66","tid":1051614,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"咁夜訓會唔會傷聲"},{"pid":"70f58d5988365d016aba70e40ad53fafa12b1bff","tid":1051614,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"點樣唱到高音啲"},{"pid":"f9f3a8c1ee586cb12e64730d2d4deb508c63174a","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29c75d32666273b042061454675237a56bd4ca86","tid":1051614,"uid":110519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"你係混音派 定真 假音斷層派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T18:01:12.000Z","msg":"um...<br />\n人人都唔同結構<br />\n定死咗一派好易鑽牛角尖<br />\n我自己鍾意咩都聽下學下"},{"pid":"c48ea81cea9ab4fe8f2a8167dc8b915d1f9ec823","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8485f553a7e7bec2e2fc1795655b2c6f492cc66","tid":1051614,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"咁夜訓會唔會傷聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T18:01:47.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n但攰會控制唔到把聲"},{"pid":"0490e7eaace03379d815af2adcba4c905c2500d0","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f58d5988365d016aba70e40ad53fafa12b1bff","tid":1051614,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"點樣唱到高音啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"咩為之高音？<br />\n例如有人覺得G4好高<br />\n有人覺得F5先叫高<br />\n所以高音要睇你個range本身去到邊<br />\n先答到大概點去唱某一個音<br />\n<br />\n不過初學都係建議練好假聲先<br />\n等聲帶有好嘅基礎先慢慢學混音（真假混聲）去唱bridge（真假區域）以上嘅音"},{"pid":"320b77aff88480c42452d7c733674acdbf1aa138","tid":1051614,"uid":150689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T18:53:30.000Z","msg":"唱k唱高音點先唔刺耳"},{"pid":"c7899e9b7e96de553ad530023ec8dc293577bd5e","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"320b77aff88480c42452d7c733674acdbf1aa138","tid":1051614,"uid":150689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T18:53:30.000Z","msg":"唱k唱高音點先唔刺耳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T19:00:48.000Z","msg":"呢個涉及到硬件問題<br />\n但呢個有排講 所以唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n刺耳呢個係主觀藝術美感問題<br />\n呢樣都唔講<br />\n<br />\n如果真係識緊某啲偏自己高音就會刺耳<br />\n就練厚啲自己把聲<br />\n<br />\n但 係<br />\n刺耳唔一定代表唔好<br />\n呢個係同風格有關<br />\n你把聲偏但又死都要唱抒情歌<br />\n咁樣冇得搞<br />\n<br />\n所以係咪代表即刻要練厚把聲唱歌就會好聽啲？未必<br />\n其實好多問題係interrelated <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1913bb4e95b38ddff8d3cee10072cef7707d670a","tid":1051614,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T19:18:06.000Z","msg":"同埋個鼻十日有八日都塞 好難用到頭腔共嗚 有冇solution 平時亦好多鼻水流到喉"},{"pid":"1083f05ad69c712fa0a3771c9de754c141c6a9a1","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1913bb4e95b38ddff8d3cee10072cef7707d670a","tid":1051614,"uid":127905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T19:18:06.000Z","msg":"同埋個鼻十日有八日都塞 好難用到頭腔共嗚 有冇solution 平時亦好多鼻水流到喉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T19:28:25.000Z","msg":"有啲同學仔會咁<br />\n鼻嘅問題好難搞<br />\n真係要由身體著手<br />\n睇醫生 洗鼻 食藥咩都好<br />\n個鼻塞咗會好影響唱歌<br />\n<br />\n呢個真係唔係我嘅範圍"},{"pid":"52f6d549a524e034172de774561cec078d35342b","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T19:29:08.000Z","msg":"俾個讚嚟我自j下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9150ab89e74f887f0dcd2f5849f350f778352e52","tid":1051614,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T19:40:18.000Z","msg":"點樣唱好個音準？"},{"pid":"0709de4d7c1b43cd92871b65930424e190bfb231","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9150ab89e74f887f0dcd2f5849f350f778352e52","tid":1051614,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T19:40:18.000Z","msg":"點樣唱好個音準？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T20:02:59.000Z","msg":"聽 <br />\n聽電子琴 跟住個音唱<br />\n<br />\n唱<br />\n對住個tuner(手機免費果啲就得）<br />\n男由G3左右逐個逐個唱準到E4<br />\n然後慢慢轉假聲再逐個逐個唱上去<br />\n女由C4左右開始<br />\n<br />\n用耳聽 用口唱 再用耳聽下自己準唔準<br />\n不斷細心觀察"},{"pid":"162e49616fa50f1bf517044b8ec50b14bbe9e829","tid":1051614,"uid":119212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T22:20:27.000Z","msg":"利申新手 求基本野開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf7dc3e8040abc34b772fd9cb7e7a121b31856e","tid":1051614,"uid":152260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T22:31:31.000Z","msg":"點為之&quot;用丹田&quot;唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51b1abdfa123618da1cbe783595c4a648844112","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162e49616fa50f1bf517044b8ec50b14bbe9e829","tid":1051614,"uid":119212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T22:20:27.000Z","msg":"利申新手 求基本野開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"基本都係練好音準同拍子先<br />\n所有嘢都係後話<br />\n真聲 假聲要可以運用自如<br />\n大部份歌需要唱得連貫 盡量做好連貫呢件事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddaca679c91110286c8d3a4c05627e941b2485a8","tid":1051614,"uid":213841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:53:43.000Z","msg":"A4極限 有咩練習可以練穩啲同高啲？"},{"pid":"80547215c5f0fcd36d15d2d7be1b42420a654f66","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcf7dc3e8040abc34b772fd9cb7e7a121b31856e","tid":1051614,"uid":152260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T22:31:31.000Z","msg":"點為之&quot;用丹田&quot;唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"簡單講 這是謬誤<br />\n沒有丹田 亦不需要丹田<br />\n九成九問題係聲帶閉合控制得唔好 <br />\n冇唔夠氣呢個問題 <br />\n<br />\n有一啲所謂唱歌老師教吸氣教個幾兩個鐘 <br />\n說話我就唔講到咁盡啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923296b709943c9d234960d32abfac60f79f2d3a","tid":1051614,"uid":114955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddaca679c91110286c8d3a4c05627e941b2485a8","tid":1051614,"uid":213841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:53:43.000Z","msg":"A4極限 有咩練習可以練穩啲同高啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:03:38.000Z","msg":"睇你range 有人高啲有人低啲<br />\n如果真係重有空間練上去<br />\n盡量唔好嗌<br />\n盡量keep喉核喺偏中間位置<br />\n下巴唔好收緊<br />\n盡量個感覺要通透個頭<br />\n唔好谷住谷住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94df6c1205b6e26941a9f0776fa83de88aef325c","tid":1051614,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"有冇歌仔聽吓"},{"pid":"0f74bf27f7bd180d188ce1308863b548c3075782","tid":1051614,"uid":145408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"有冇教過學生<br />\n唱既時候低8度唱自己唔知"},{"pid":"5f8b64c6bdda46a19ba45c051fa164b8947b7484","tid":1051614,"uid":218626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T11:35:08.000Z","msg":"我想問下咩叫&quot;外國新派流行聲樂法&quot;🙏"}]}